WEBVTT

00:01.502 --> 00:02.435
Pizza, pizza.

00:02.503 --> 00:04.404
[laughing]

00:08.241 --> 00:11.344
Guess what I got for
Synclaire's bachelorette party.

00:14.080 --> 00:16.850
"'The Men Chippendales
Doesn't Want You To Know About.'

00:16.917 --> 00:18.585
featuring Cappachino‐‐"

00:18.652 --> 00:20.754
‐ And Nature Boy! Yes!"
‐ "And Nature Boy!"

00:20.821 --> 00:22.322
Best thing, it's in 3D.

00:24.224 --> 00:26.727
We can't let Synclaire see this
unless we check it out first.

00:26.793 --> 00:28.461
To make sure
that it's not too nasty.

00:28.529 --> 00:30.163
Yes. Come on, girl.

00:30.230 --> 00:32.533
Hey, Khadijah,
um, you got those linens

00:32.598 --> 00:34.701
that you said I could borrow
for my little brother.

00:34.768 --> 00:36.703
Oh, dear God,
she's nesting on them.

00:38.639 --> 00:40.941
‐ Well, if you'll‐‐
‐ Oh, okay.

00:43.877 --> 00:47.781
If, uh, you'll excuse me, I have
to call the Crestmark Club

00:47.848 --> 00:50.016
to make sure everything is cool
for Overton's bachelor party.

00:50.083 --> 00:52.586
The Crestmark Club? Hold up,
I thought Overton and Synclaire

00:52.653 --> 00:54.454
wanted to keep
their party simple.

00:54.521 --> 00:55.622
Baby, what could be simpler

00:55.689 --> 00:58.291
than 15 people catering
to Overton's every whim?

00:58.358 --> 01:00.534
Sixteen including
the butter carver. Oho!

01:00.601 --> 01:02.302
That is so you.

01:02.368 --> 01:05.271
You're‐you're planning a party
where a guy is carving butter.

01:05.337 --> 01:08.608
Overton wants a party where
women are covered in butter.

01:10.043 --> 01:13.079
Look, this is an important
rite of passage for Overton

01:13.146 --> 01:14.948
and I just want him to know
that he chose

01:15.015 --> 01:17.951
the best man
to be his best man, alright?

01:20.253 --> 01:22.455
Man, look, as the maid of honor

01:22.523 --> 01:24.758
I gotta come up with
something more elaborate.

01:24.825 --> 01:26.593
Something more memorable.

01:26.660 --> 01:29.029
Something more better.

01:29.095 --> 01:31.464
You want more better?

01:31.532 --> 01:34.635
Just wait till Nature Boy jumps
off the screen into your lap.

